                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">GA4</div>
                                <div>Google-hosted</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">PostHog</div>
                                <div>Full (self-host/cloud)</div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Privacy Law Fit</td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">GA4</div>
                                <div>Google-defined policies</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">PostHog</div>
                                <div>Strong (Canada/EU)</div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Event Tracking Setup</td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">GA4</div>
                                <div>Manual, needs GTM/Measurement Prot.</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">PostHog</div>
                                <div>Autocapture + API + SDK</div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Session Replay/Heatmap</td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">GA4</div>
                                <div>Requires third-party tools</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">PostHog</div>
                                <div>Built-in</div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Feature Flags/A/B Test</td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">GA4</div>
                                <div>Needs another product</div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">PostHog</div>
                                <div>Built-in</div>
                            </td>
