        <div id="cms-modal" class="fixed hidden lg:items-center items-end lg:justify-center justify-end h-full w-full bg-neutral-800/10 backdrop-blur-xs z-50 transition-all">
            <div class="square-card lg:h-auto w-auto h-[85vh] lg:overflow-hidden overflow-y-auto">
                <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 flex-wrap items-center justify-center mb-9">
                    <div class="text-lg underline">Sanity vs Payload</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:bg-transparent lg:border-0 square-card p-0 max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
                    <table class="w-full text-left lg:text-lg border-collapse">
                        <thead class="my-6 hidden lg:table-header-group">
                            <tr>
                                <th></th>
                                <th>Sanity</th>
                                <th>Payload CMS</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Pricing</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Free tier: includes up to 20 user seats, 2 permission roles,
                                        2 datasets, unlimited content types and locales.
                                        Growth tier: $15 USD/user/month
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Free OSS self-host: unlimited users, permission roles, datasets, locales, etc</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Ongoing Dev Dependency</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Low; managed cloud, minimal DevOps</div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Medium; self-host requires infrastructure management</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Features</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        Visual/live editing, asset management, localization, publishing workflows, versioning, and more
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        Near feature-parity: Asset management, localization, publishing workflows, versioning, and more
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Data Ownership</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>GDPR/SOC2 compliant, cloud-hosted database, albeit with full data export</div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Complete control; self-hosted DB (MongoDB/Postgres/etc)</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Hosting and Scalability</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Self-hostable, OSS client, with a cloud-hosted database behind a global CDN</div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Self/cloud client and database; manual scaling, full perf control</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Community and Support</td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Sanity
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Large (180k+ devs), docs/plugins, enterprise SLAs</div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400 lg:hidden mb-2">
                                        Payload CMS
                                    </div>
                                    <div>Growing (30k+ stars), active GitHub, recent Figma acquisition</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Summary</td>
                                <td colspan="2">Payload has near feature parity with Sanity, and offers a similar content editing experience. Though
                                    Sanity offers a more seamless setup and long term maintenance with managed infrastructure. We choose
                                    Payload when pricing and data ownership are upmost considerations.
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <style>
                    @reference "../../styles/global.css";

                    #cms-modal table td {
                        @apply p-3 border-b border-neutral-700;
                    }

                    @media (min-width: 1023px) {
                        #cms-modal table tr:last-child td, #cms-modal table tr:last-child th {
                            @apply border-b-0;
                        }
                    }

                    #cms-modal table th {
                        @apply p-3 pb-6 font-medium;
                    }

                    /*#cms-modal table tr :nth-child(3), #cms-modal table th:nth-child(3) {
